      <h1 class="project-name">Abu-dju.GitHub.io</h1>
      <h2 class="project-tagline">This repository tries to gather some rare and yet useful dictionaries that have fallen in the public domain (for instance: Edward William Lane&#39;s Arabic-English Lexicon).<br><br>
      Ce site essaie de rassembler quelques rares mais importants dictionnnaires qui sont tombés dans le domaine public (par exemple: Edward William Lane&#39;s Arabic-English Lexicon</h2>
